We retrieved 33 candidate genes (Table 3) within 10 Mbp up- and downstream of 23 associated SNP QTL (quantitative trait locus) positions using the ZmB73 RefGen v2 database (https://www.maizegdb.org/gbrowse). These genes have previously been annotated with a plant defence function. The phenotypic variation (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
